title: webinjection
extract: The trojan is able to inject code, such as JavaScript, into the browser to interact with the website content and perform various actions. ... In the case of some banking trojans, the webinject configuration file contains the true attack code, meaning that it is the one that will ultimately bring revenue to the botmaster.Oct 23, 2014
